    "description": "We at Neuland Laboratories Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Consultant Physician based out of Varanasi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Neuland Laboratories Holdings Services:\nNeuland Laboratories Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Neuland Laboratories Holdings Services!",
